    <tr> 
     <th style="text-align: center;" colspan="2"> <h2>Honed Bolt</h2> </th> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td style="text-align: center;" colspan="2"><img style="width: 200px; height: 200px;" title="Honed Bolt" src="/file/Elden-Ring/honed bolt_incantation_elden_ring_wiki_guide_200px.png" alt="honed bolt incantation elden ring wiki guide 200px" width="200" height="200"></td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td>Spell Type</td> 
     <td><a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Dragon Cult Incantations" href="/Dragon+Cult+Incantations" target="">Dragon Cult Incantations</a></td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td>FP Cost 12</td> 
     <td>Slots Used 1</td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td colspan="2"><img title="item_effect_icon_elden_ring_wiki_guide_18px" src="/file/Elden-Ring/item_effects_icon_elden_ring_wiki_guide_55px_18px.png" alt="item effects icon elden ring wiki guide 55px 18px" width="18" height="18">Effect 
      <div class="lineleft">
        Strikes foe with lightning bolt from above 
      </div> <br><img style="float: left;" title="Attributes Requirement" src="/file/Elden-Ring/attributes-required-elden-ring-wiki-guide-18.png" alt="attributes required elden ring wiki guide 18" width="18" height="18">Requires 
      <div class="lineleft"> 
       <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Intelligence" href="/Intelligence" target="">Intelligence</a> 0 
       <br> 
       <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Faith" href="/Faith" target="">Faith</a> 24 
       <br> 
       <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Arcane" href="/Arcane" target="">Arcane</a>&nbsp;0 
      </div> </td> 
    </tr> 
   </tbody> 
  </table> 
 </div> 
</div> 
<p><strong>Honed Bolt </strong> is an <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Incantations" href="/Incantations" target="">Incantation</a> in <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Wiki" href="/Elden+Ring+Wiki">Elden Ring</a>. <strong>Honed Bolt spell</strong> conjures bolts of lightning that impact nearby foes.</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<div class="lineleft"> 
 <p><em>One of the incantations of the capital's ancient dragon cult.</em><br><em><br>Summons a bolt of lightning to strike foes from above.<br>This incantation can be cast repeatedly.</em></p> 
 <p><em>Long ago, Godwyn the Golden defeated the ancient dragon</em><em> Fortissax, and befriended his fallen foe â€” an event that gave rise to</em><em> the ancient dragon cult in the capital.</em></p> 
</div> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Where to find Honed Bolt</h3> 
<p>Where to find <strong>Honed Bolt </strong>:</p> 
<ul> 
 <li>Purchase from <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Brother Corhyn" href="/Brother+Corhyn" target="">Brother Corhyn</a> or&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Miriel Pastor of Vows" href="/Miriel+Pastor+of+Vows">Miriel, Pastor of Vows</a> after giving either the <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Dragon Cult Prayerbook" href="/Dragon+Cult+Prayerbook" target="">Dragon Cult Prayerbook</a></li> 
</ul> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Elden Ring&nbsp;Honed Bolt Guide</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li>Stamina Cost: 29</li> 
 <li>One of the <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Dragon Cult Incantations" href="/Dragon+Cult+Incantations">Dragon Cult Incantations</a> and is boosted by the <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Gravel Stone Seal" href="/Gravel+Stone+Seal">Gravel Stone Seal</a></li> 
 <li>Deals lightning damage</li> 
 <li>While this incantation can be cast quickly and repeatedly, the initial startup time is quite lengthy.</li> 
 <li>A single instance of this spell will be outperformed by <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Lightning Spear" href="/Lightning+Spear">Lightning Spear</a>, but repeated casts will improve its DPS quickly.</li> 
</ul> 
